      "Pick a flower from the garden in the morning: put it in a small glass or egg cup of water. A single fresh flower picked by hand is more personal than anything bought.",
      "Lay the tray with care: use a nice placemat or cloth napkin. Arrange things neatly. Place the flower and card prominently. Presentation communicates effort and love.",
