      "Add extras: fold in glitter for sparkle. Knead in a drop of food colouring for colour. Scented conditioner or a few drops of essential oil gives a calming aromatic dimension.",
      "Test the properties: press a thumb print - it holds the impression. Roll a snake - it holds its shape. Pinch it - clean edges. Tear it - it tears cleanly without sticking.",
      "Build with it: make animals, food items, flowers, or geometric shapes. The non-sticky quality allows detailed work without frustration.",
      "Compare to other doughs: handle regular playdough and this dough back to back. Notice the texture difference. What makes each unique? What is each best for?",
