      "Understand the limits: this dough does not dry into a permanent form. Pieces crumble when left to dry. It is a play medium, not a sculpting medium.",
      "Use fresh: the dough is best the day it is made. The conditioner can separate over time, changing the texture. Make a fresh batch whenever the best sensory experience is needed."
